properties.Name: VendorType
properties.Description:
A categorization of Vendors based upon whether they manufacture and supply the product (OEM), add value to the product and supply it (VAR), resell the product (Reseller), wholesale the product (Wholesaler) etc.

Ex :
- OEM
- VAR
- Reseller
- Wholesaler

Columns.Name: VendorTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Vendor Type.

Columns.Name: VendorTypeName
Columns.Description: The name of the Vendor Type.

Columns.Name: VendorTypeDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Vendor Type.
